-- Mr Price Full-Year Earnings Per Share Rose as Much as 23%
-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 2012-05-02T06:04:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-02/mr-price-full-year-earnings-per-share-rose-as-much-as-23-.html
Mr Price Group Ltd. (MPC) , a South African
retailer, said earnings per share in the 52 weeks through March
rose 18 percent to 23 percent compared with the 53 weeks through
April 2 last year.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
